- The integer matrix parameter `mat` must not be null.
- The integer parameter `k` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100.
- The length of the integer matrix result is equal to the length of the integer matrix parameter `mat`.
- The length of each row in the integer matrix result is equal to the length of each row in the integer matrix parameter `mat`.
- Each element `answer[i][j]` in the integer matrix result is the sum of all elements `mat[r][c]` where `i - k <= r <= i + k`, `j - k <= c <= j + k`, and `(r, c)` is a valid position in the matrix.